      <para id="id1171388081422">That is good work, but lets take it one step further now…</para>
      <para id="id1171377226727">REWRITE THE SENTENCES ABOVE USING QUOTATION (SPEECH) MARKS</para>
      <para id="id1171380826006">e.g. Deb shouted, "Mind that dog, Sally!"</para>
      <para id="id1171385098477">Remember to use words such as <emphasis effect="bold">shouted, asked, replied, answered, warned, offered, moaned, said</emphasis>.</para>
